        "name": "Multi-site VAD registry observational study",
        "activityType": "observational-study",
        "description": "Retrospective prospective observational study drawing on de-identified VAD patient records from five academic medical centres. Operating condition data were extracted from device logs; hemolysis index was derived from quarterly plasma-free hemoglobin laboratory values. Propensity-score matching was applied to reduce confounding by patient comorbidities and anticoagulation regimen. No active manipulation of flow rate or speed was performed; all measurements reflect clinical operating conditions as set by treating clinicians.",
